    "4007218": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Leon",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "I'm sorry you have to keep seeing me in such a wretched state. I suppose I'm still not good enough to play the role of a qualified Nachtraben Ritter..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "\"Play the role\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "I'm ashamed to admit it, but I'm not a real knight... rather, I'm a new actor who recently landed a job to play the role of a knight in a theater troupe!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's not really something to be smug about."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Ah, well, you see, that's where you're mistaken! Theater is an essential part of Immernachtreich's culture. A fantastic theatrical performance is the greatest tribute we can pay to Her Highness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Oh, so this is your local culture?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Exactly! So I'm delighted that I got to play the knight!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Why does the Prinzessin enjoy the theater so much?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Her Highness once said, \"Celebrate me by staging a play in the wilderness. Bow down to me, and bring me beautiful dreams in return for everlasting glory within the eternal darkness.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "I believe it is because Her Highness appreciates true art, and can also sense emotions hidden deep within the souls of humankind."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "The crystallization and sublime expression of emotion is the heart of theater. People who truly understand theater always have a beautiful, sensitive heart, filled with a rich array of emotion."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "...So that's how it is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Thank you for your answer, Sir Knight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "O—Oh! Th—Thank you so much for calling me a knight!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "So, basking still in this honor, I will be off to my battleground. May we meet again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hopefully not... Be more careful in the future!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Oh, and please remember the password to unlock the gate, \"Upon my command, spread your wings and take flight.\""
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
