    "4007213": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We're back again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I believe we have just witnessed the true nature of the wicked dragon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "*sigh* This is something I am all too familiar with. There are always people who believe that our passions are a waste of time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Huh? You're—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arnold",
                    "T": "Ask-Me-For-Directions Arnold."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "I mean, you're back, why?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arnold",
                    "T": "Oh, I came because I bet you'd be looking for the third volume of \"Hymn of the Holy Land.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Well, you bet right on that front..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arnold",
                    "T": "You need not do anything for me, my dear lady. The opportunity to behold your beauty is the finest reward I could ask for. I shall give you the answer you seek."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arnold",
                    "T": "The third volume of \"Hymn of the Holy Land\" can be found on the top floor of the royal castle."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Is it guarded by anyone?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arnold",
                    "T": "Oh, oh, but of course, sir. What sort of a question is that? No nation would treat its most treasured books as if they were just cast out into the wilderness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "That means we will still find Nachtraben guards stationed there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arnold",
                    "T": "It is a citizen's utmost honor to guard the sacred scriptures. But it matters not. I'm quite sure the fine lady merely seeks to peruse them, and has no malicious intentions."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arnold",
                    "T": "Your face is captivating and full of wisdom, and the company you keep appears to be heroes of some renown. I have the utmost faith that you will be able to comprehend the meaning behind the stories in our sacred scriptures."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arnold",
                    "T": "Her Highness's accomplishments were documented by Oz, the Great Sekretär, and became great treasures of the Immernachtreich. I wish Her Highness joy and happiness every time I read those books."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "4007302": {
        "Desc": "Look for the third volume of \"Hymn of the Holy Land\"",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Solemn Raven",
                    "T": "Stop! Ugh, it's you guys again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's your problem? We're the Prinzessin's personal retainers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Severe Raven",
                    "T": "Cut the lies! Her Highness doesn't keep company with nobodies like you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Oh really? Are you prepared to take responsibility for what you just said?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Severe Raven",
                    "T": "I'll say it again. Her Highness doesn't keep company with—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Who are these \"nobodies\" you speak of?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Solemn Raven",
                    "T": "Her Highness and Sir Oz!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "I must say, guards, it's immensely disrespectful of you to make such remarks to the retainers of the Immernachtreich."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Hmph. How dare you treat one's handpicked retainers with such disdain? Begone!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Solemn Raven",
                    "T": "But..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Don't you \"but\" me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Severe Raven",
                    "T": "Y—Yes, Your Highness!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Fischl, Oz, you're back in the crew!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Hmph, you may consider that the case for the time being."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "What mein Fräulein means is that it took us a long time to reach this place. She couldn't bear to leave you all here, even though she did not wish to confront this mirage."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Didn't wanna confront it, huh? Sounds like Mona was right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It felt like we were peeking into your diary."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "...Nonsense. Despite the existing threats, the unrivaled glory of the Immernachtreich would not exist in this world if I, the Prinzessin, were the sort of person who could be easily swayed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "What mein Fräulein means to say is that there are other troubles in this area."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Troubles? Have you run into anything dangerous?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "...Um... this matter can be revisited later. For now, let us proceed with more important work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Let's get this show on the road! The book's right in front of us, let's not just stand here."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
