    "4007313": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Leon",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Fella, if you want to survive and thrive, you should be more careful next time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "A successful journey requires perseverance, courage, as well as a keen sense of danger. You have the first two, but in the future, please strive to be more vigilant."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "I shall remember your words for the rest of my life. But it is time to say our final goodbye."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "You may not have noticed, but the weather has improved, and the sea has become pleasant and calm... We have awaited this day for a long time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "You may be amazed that someone as reckless as me could become an actor, but please believe me when I say it's not by chance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Every Nachtraben is looking for a way to contribute to the world. We just want to find our place, our destiny. We were born to seek the roles that fate has assigned us to play."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "You may not be aware that \"Hymn of the Holy Land\" is also a book of prophecies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Prophecy? But Paimon thought it was a sacred scripture?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Yes, it is. Hundreds of years ago, the Immernachtreich was engulfed by a menacing shadow, but our ruler stood by and did nothing, as if she had lost interest in ruling the kingdom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Soon after, Oz, the Great Sekretär, appeared among us. He brought us the sacred scriptures, and a most encouraging prophecy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "That prophecy is just as it's described in the book, and predicts a blessed future for the Immernachtreich. As a result, we became convinced that the gloomy skies would eventually clear, and we have been eagerly waiting for that blessed day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "The Soteria... the Prinzessin der Verurteilung. She will eventually remember the paradise of the Immernachtreich, and on that day, we will devote to her the plays that were promised in the prophecy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "That is why I have stepped forward to take on the role of a warrior. I'd do whatever it takes to prove my devotion to her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Y—Your Highness?!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, right, yeah she was lurking in the back when we rescued you for some reason..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "My citizen, thy will is strong enough to sunder the wicked dragon's wings. I shall now receive thy blessing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "It is my utmost honor!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Thou hast done well. 'Tis also most evident that thou dost possess the virtues of a knight. Go, take thy position, and wait for the performance to begin."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "We commend your unfaltering loyalty to Her Highness. Her Highness will now lead her retainers into battle against the shadow that plagues the Immernachtreich."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "...Thank you, Your Highness, and thank you, everyone. In that case, I will take my leave!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Leon",
                    "T": "Oh, by the way, please keep in mind that the password for the gate ahead is \"Sieh an, mein Sommernachtgarten!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's confused. What were you guys role-playing just now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Is there not a single one of my lords and ladies who understood my precepts? Fools."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "What mein Fräulein means to say is that you are all rather stupid."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Yeah, you didn't need to translate that!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I suppose this is the important business Her Highness warned us about earlier."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Let's get this over with!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Wait! What is it? What's happening?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
